title: CNN God's Warriors Part 1 - God's Jewish Warriors.wmv
description: CNN will premiere a six-hour television event across its U.S. and international networks in August on the impact of the rise of religious fundamentalism as a powerful political force in three faiths: Judaism, Islam and Christianity.  CNN chief international correspondent Christiane Amanpour traveled the world to report CNN Presents: God&#039;s Warriors.  The U.S.premiere airs Tuesday, Aug. 21, through Thursday, Aug. 23, from 9 p.m. to 11 p.m. each night (ET/PT).
